          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Support Recovery from Addiction Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill requires states to expend at least 10% of their Substance Abuse Prevention and Treatment Block Grants on recovery support services for individuals with substance use disorders.</p> <p><br> </p>]]>
        </text>
